      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The student must have secured 60% or more marks in the 12th standard.\n1. The girl must reside in a rural area and possess a &quot;Gaon Ki Beti&quot; (Daughter of the Village) certificate.\n1. She must be enrolled in a recognized institution for higher education.\n\n<br>\n\n",
